meta_info.description: Step back in time with the 'On This Day in History' plugin, where you can uncover the significant events that shaped our world on the current date across the annals of history. From breakthroughs in science to pivotal moments in culture, discover a daily dose of historical facts right at your fingertips.
meta_info.name: On This Day in History
